# AgentFrame Consulting Prep — environment template.
# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill only what you use. Everything is OPTIONAL — the system runs without it.
# (Your coding agent provides the LLM. These keys power the optional Composio connector tools.)

# --- Composio: one connection, 100+ tools (Google Docs, Gmail, Calendar, Drive, ...) ---
# OPTIONAL + manual: Composio is NOT wired in automatically. You connect it once per machine — its MCP URL is
# generated per-user, so it can't ship pre-configured. Full setup (SDK install, OAuth, claude mcp add) is in:
#   library/context/connectors.md
# Get an `ak_…` key from https://app.composio.dev, then follow that doc.
COMPOSIO_API_KEY=
USER_ID=
